OL,3,CFormer MP Crispin Blunt pleads guilty
OL,4,Cto possession of drugs
OL,6,FFormer MP Crispin Blunt has pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to possessing illegal drugs
OL,8,Fincluding cannabis and crystal meth.
OL,10,FThe 65-year-old former justice
OL,11,Fminister appeared at Westminster
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday to
OL,13,Fadmit four drugs charges, which stem
OL,14,Ffrom a raid on his home in Horley,
OL,15,FSurrey, on October 25 2023.
OL,17,FBlunt was in possession of the
OL,18,Fchemical drug GBL, a sedative, as well
OL,19,Fas cannabis, methamphetamine and
OL,20,Fmethylamphetamine ` which is commonly
OL,21,Fknown as crystal meth.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
