CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774631480
OL,3,CFormer MP Crispin Blunt pleads guilty
OL,4,Cto possession of drugs
OL,6,FHe has pleaded guilty to one count of
OL,7,Fpossessing class A drugs and three
OL,8,Fcharges of possession of class B drugs.
OL,10,FThe drugs were found when Blunt, who
OL,11,Frepresented Reigate in Parliament
OL,12,Fbetween 1997 and 2024, was being
OL,13,Finvestigated on suspicion of rape.
OL,15,FAfter an 18-month investigation,
OL,16,FSurrey Police announced in May last
OL,17,Fyear that there would be no further
OL,18,Faction on the rape allegation due to
OL,19,Finsufficient evidence.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
