PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774631480
OL,3,CFormer MP Crispin Blunt pleads guilty
OL,4,Cto possession of drugs
OL,6,FBlunt, wearing a charcoal-grey suit,
OL,7,Fwhite shirt, and purple tie, is
OL,8,Frepresenting himself in the criminal
OL,9,Fcourt proceedings.
OL,11,FBlunt represented the Conservative
OL,12,FParty in Parliament. He served in
OL,13,FDavid Cameron's government as
OL,14,Fparliamentary under-secretary of state
OL,15,Ffor prisons and youth justice from
OL,16,F2010 to 2012, and went on to chair the
OL,17,FForeign Affairs Committee from 2015
OL,18,Funtil 2017.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
