OL,3,CFormer MP Crispin Blunt pleads guilty
OL,4,Cto possession of drugs
OL,6,FHe lost the Tory whip in October 2023
OL,7,Fwhen he was first arrested by police,
OL,8,Fand stood down from Parliament at the
OL,9,F2024 general election.
OL,11,FPrior to entering Parliament, Blunt
OL,12,Fwas a graduate of the Sandhurst
OL,13,FMilitary Academy and spent more than a
OL,14,Fdecade as an officer in the British
OL,15,FArmy.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
